<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Support Request Received</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f4f4; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; }
    .header { background-color: #1a365d; padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
    .header h1 { color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 28px; }
    .content { padding: 40px 30px; }
    .content h2 { color: #1a365d; margin-top: 0; }
    .content p { color: #4a5568; line-height: 1.6; }
    .details { background-color: #f7fafc; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .details table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
    .details td { padding: 8px 0; color: #4a5568; }
    .details td:first-child { font-weight: 600; color: #1a365d; width: 120px; }
    .footer { background-color: #edf2f7; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #718096; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>{{appName}}</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Support Request Received</h2>
      <p>Hi {{firstName}},</p>
      <p>We have received your support request and our team will review it shortly. Here are the details:</p>

      <div class="details">
        <table>
          <tr>
            <td>Ticket ID</td>
            <td>{{ticketId}}</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Subject</td>
            <td>{{subject}}</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Category</td>
            <td>{{category}}</td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </div>

      <p>We aim to respond to all support requests as soon as possible. You can check the status of your request at any time from the Help & Support section in your account.</p>

      <p>Thank you for your patience.</p>

      <p>Best regards,<br>The {{appName}} Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{year}} {{appName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>This email was sent because you submitted a support request.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
